{"tid":848044,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"轉貼 屯門NAPA再新增取消交易個案","createTime":"2018-10-04T15:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T16:00:15.000Z","uid":62935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39a26416c3d736bc5cf65698bf4ee3effad5acd3","tid":848044,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"屯門NAPA再新增取消交易個案，有買家放棄51.6萬訂金撻訂離場。綜合EPRC（經濟地產庫）及成交紀錄冊顯示，NAPA 6座9樓B室，實用面積839平方呎，一名陳氏買家於今年3月下旬以1,033.1萬元入市，採用90天二按，已付5%訂金，剛於本周二（10月2日），即本地銀行加息後，終止買賣合約，撻訂收場，料損失逾51萬訂金。"},{"pid":"993f6a16368285f1d3e8b559ae61c6d40dd4d7da","tid":848044,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2175714/屯門NAPA買家3月逾千萬入市%20本月初撻訂棄上會\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2175714%2F%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80NAPA%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B63%E6%9C%88%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%2520%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%88%9D%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%E6%A3%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%83&d=Fc3vIDUpqBy7Qb%2BnqzevaZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2b87f1b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2175714/屯門NAPA買家3月逾千萬入市%20本月初撻訂棄上會</a>"},{"pid":"5b882cd43b8f84de99c39d5bec78087b3f2ac8ca","tid":848044,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"屯門唔計"},{"pid":"e17570aee36e353010bd0d34f06dbccc70ac7bfd","tid":848044,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"450c50510e224ee1cbba53d773d4f9d41fa4577a","tid":848044,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"撻訂買上源?"}]}